hackathon-description-text: A 16 city hackathon/startup weekend where teams can collaborate globally.
hackathon-eligibility: Anyone who has registered for our event
hackathon-requirements:
-prototype
-business plan
-team bios, team contact info
-any related video or images

hackathon-judging-criteria.judging-criterion:
-how will you acquire customers?
-what is the revenue model?
-what is the marketing plan?
-did you collaborate with team members in a another city?

hackathon-description-header: Startup weekend for Pakistan in 16 cities
